<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/head') %>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main>
        <section class="container-custom py-10 md:py-16">
            <div class="style-shell px-6 py-8 md:px-10 md:py-12">
                <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
                    <div class="absolute -top-16 right-[-3rem] h-44 w-44 rounded-full bg-gold/20 blur-3xl"></div>
                    <div class="absolute left-[-2rem] top-1/3 h-52 w-52 rounded-full bg-accent-purple/15 blur-3xl"></div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-[-4rem] right-1/4 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-light-gold/35 blur-3xl"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <header class="mb-12 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] lg:items-end">
                        <div class="max-w-3xl">
                            <span class="style-kicker mb-6">Modernized brand direction</span>
                            <h1 class="font-cormorant text-5xl font-medium leading-[0.92] text-accent-purple md:text-7xl">
                                A softer, richer design language for the next chapter of Vagus Skool.
                            </h1>
                            <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-dark-text/85 md:text-xl">
                                This concept keeps your signature lavender and gold palette, but updates the site with more depth, refined spacing, layered glass surfaces, and an editorial rhythm that feels current on the modern web.
                            </p>

                            <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                                <span class="style-chip">Glass surfaces</span>
                                <span class="style-chip">Editorial typography</span>
                                <span class="style-chip">Warmer gradients</span>
                                <span class="style-chip">Premium CTA treatment</span>
                            </div>

                            <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
                                <a href="https://www.skool.com/vagus" class="golden-button text-center">Enter the community</a>
                                <a href="/courses" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-accent-purple/15 bg-white/70 px-8 py-4 text-lg text-accent-purple shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/40 hover:text-gold">
                                    Explore learning paths
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-1">
                            <div class="style-metric">
                                <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/70">Visual mood</p>
                                <p class="mt-3 font-cormorant text-3xl text-accent-purple">Calm, elevated, and experiential</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="style-metric">
                                <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/70">Design move</p>
                                <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-relaxed text-dark-text/80">
                                    Blend wellness softness with a premium product feel instead of a simple marketing-page layout.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </header>

                    <section class="mb-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
                        <article class="style-panel">
                            <div class="mb-6 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
                                <div>
                                    <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/70">Hero system</p>
                                    <h2 class="mt-3 font-cormorant text-3xl font-medium text-accent-purple md:text-4xl">Lighter, more cinematic first impressions</h2>
                                </div>
                                <span class="rounded-full bg-gold/15 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-accent-purple">01</span>
                            </div>

                            <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
                                <div class="rounded-2xl bg-accent-purple px-5 py-6 text-soft-white shadow-xl">
                                    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-white/70">Primary</p>
                                    <p class="mt-4 font-cormorant text-3xl">Statement serif headlines</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-accent-purple/10 bg-white/80 px-5 py-6">
                                    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/65">Secondary</p>
                                    <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-dark-text/80">Clean supporting copy with more whitespace and less density.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gold/20 bg-gold/10 px-5 py-6">
                                    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/65">Accent</p>
                                    <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-dark-text/80">Gold becomes more intentional and premium, not overly loud.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </article>

                        <aside class="style-panel bg-gradient-to-br from-white/80 via-white/65 to-accent-purple/10">
                            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/70">Principles</p>
                            <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-lg text-dark-text/85">
                                <li class="flex gap-3">
                                    <span class="mt-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-gold"></span>
                                    <span>Increase contrast between content tiers so each section feels more intentional.</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex gap-3">
                                    <span class="mt-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-gold"></span>
                                    <span>Use rounded glass containers to add depth without leaving the existing palette behind.</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex gap-3">
                                    <span class="mt-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-gold"></span>
                                    <span>Keep the site calm and trustworthy, but make it feel more bespoke and less template-like.</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </aside>
                    </section>

                    <section class="mb-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4">
                        <article class="style-panel">
                            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/70">Typography</p>
                            <h3 class="mt-3 font-cormorant text-3xl text-accent-purple">Expressive, not ornate</h3>
                            <p class="mt-4 text-dark-text/80">Cormorant stays as the signature voice, while tighter line lengths and stronger scale create a cleaner editorial cadence.</p>
                        </article>

                        <article class="style-panel">
                            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/70">Surfaces</p>
                            <h3 class="mt-3 font-cormorant text-3xl text-accent-purple">Soft translucency</h3>
                            <p class="mt-4 text-dark-text/80">Cards use blur, luminous borders, and subtle gradients to feel tactile and premium on desktop and mobile.</p>
                        </article>

                        <article class="style-panel">
                            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/70">Content</p>
                            <h3 class="mt-3 font-cormorant text-3xl text-accent-purple">More narrative pacing</h3>
                            <p class="mt-4 text-dark-text/80">Instead of stacking similar sections, the layout alternates feature panels, stats, and calls to action to keep momentum.</p>
                        </article>

                        <article class="style-panel">
                            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/70">Calls to action</p>
                            <h3 class="mt-3 font-cormorant text-3xl text-accent-purple">Still unmistakably Vagus Skool</h3>
                            <p class="mt-4 text-dark-text/80">Your gold CTA remains the conversion anchor, but sits inside a more polished and contemporary system.</p>
                        </article>
                    </section>

                    <section class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr]">
                        <article class="style-panel bg-accent-purple text-soft-white">
                            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-white/65">Suggested direction</p>
                            <h2 class="mt-4 font-cormorant text-4xl font-medium md:text-5xl">Designed for trust, clarity, and a more premium sense of calm.</h2>
                            <p class="mt-5 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-white/85">
                                If you like this direction, the same system can be rolled across the home page, course cards, testimonials, and blog index so the whole site feels newly art directed, not just repainted.
                            </p>
                            <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
                                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/10 p-4">
                                    <p class="text-3xl font-medium text-gold">12</p>
                                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-white/70">Section patterns</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/10 p-4">
                                    <p class="text-3xl font-medium text-gold">3</p>
                                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-white/70">Surface styles</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/10 p-4">
                                    <p class="text-3xl font-medium text-gold">1</p>
                                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-white/70">Unified visual voice</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </article>

                        <article class="style-panel">
                            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/70">Page composition sample</p>
                            <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
                                <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-accent-purple/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-accent-purple/10 p-6">
                                    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/65">Feature story</p>
                                    <h3 class="mt-4 font-cormorant text-3xl text-accent-purple">The body learns through rhythm, safety, and repetition.</h3>
                                    <p class="mt-4 text-dark-text/80">Content can be presented more like guided practice and less like a list of modules, which better fits the brand and subject matter.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                                    <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-accent-purple/10 bg-white/90 p-5">
                                        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/65">Micro card</p>
                                        <p class="mt-3 text-dark-text/80">Short, high-value proof points gain more visual hierarchy.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-gold/20 bg-gold/10 p-5">
                                        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/65">Accent block</p>
                                        <p class="mt-3 text-dark-text/80">Warm highlights can guide the eye without overwhelming the page.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-accent-purple/10 bg-accent-purple/5 p-5">
                                        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-accent-purple/65">Support panel</p>
                                        <p class="mt-3 text-dark-text/80">Each component stays easy to reuse inside existing EJS templates.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
